ai-bridge

This product includes derived work from the following MIT-licensed projects:

- cpa-plugin-codexcomp (https://github.com/uf-hy/cpa-plugin-codexcomp)
  fold.go is ported near-verbatim from its fold.go (commit 26875b5). The fold
  state machine in foldstream.go is adapted from its executor.go.

- codexcomp (https://github.com/dzshzx/codexcomp)
  Original transport-agnostic fold algorithm (fold.py), from which the above
  Go port derives.

- CodexCont (https://github.com/neteroster/CodexCont)
  Original discovery of the gpt-5.5 518n-2 reasoning-truncation pattern and the
  encrypted_content replay continuation technique.

The 518n-2 truncation/degradation issue was primarily investigated and verified
by the LINUX DO community (https://linux.do).
